#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:2
msgid "CVRP Problem"
msgstr "CVRP 问题"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:5
msgid "Problem Definition"
msgstr "问题定义"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:7
msgid ""
"The **Capacitated Vehicle Routing Problem (CVRP)** is a classic "
"combinatorial optimisation problem in operations research."
msgstr "**容量限制车辆路径问题（CVRP）** 是运筹学中的经典组合优化问题。"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:11
msgid "Scenario"
msgstr "问题场景"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:13
msgid ""
"A distribution centre (depot) must deliver goods to a set of customers "
"using a fleet of vehicles:"
msgstr "一个配送中心（仓库）需要用一组车辆为多个客户配送货物："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:15
msgid "Each customer has a demand quantity"
msgstr "每个客户有一个需求量"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:16
msgid "Each vehicle has a capacity limit"
msgstr "每辆车有容量限制"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:17
msgid "Vehicles depart from the depot, serve customers, and return to the depot"
msgstr "车辆从仓库出发，服务完客户后返回仓库"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:18
msgid "Objective: minimise total travel distance"
msgstr "目标：最小化总行驶距离"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:21
msgid "Mathematical Definition"
msgstr "数学定义"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:24
msgid "Input"
msgstr "输入"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:26
msgid "Given a CVRP instance :math:`I = (G, Q, d, c)`:"
msgstr "给定一个 CVRP 实例 :math:`I = (G, Q, d, c)`："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:28
msgid "CVRP Input Parameters"
msgstr "CVRP 输入参数"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:31
msgid "Symbol"
msgstr "符号"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:32
msgid "Meaning"
msgstr "含义"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:33
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:34
msgid ":math:`G = (V, E)`"
msgstr ":math:`G = (V, E)`"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:35
msgid "Undirected graph"
msgstr "无向图"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:36
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":math:`V = \\{0, 1, \\ldots, n\\}`, node 0 is the depot, 1–n are customers"
msgstr ":math:`V = \\{0, 1, \\ldots, n\\}`，节点 0 为仓库，1–n 为客户"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:37
msgid ":math:`Q`"
msgstr ":math:`Q`"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:38
msgid "Vehicle capacity"
msgstr "车辆容量"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:39
msgid "Maximum load per vehicle"
msgstr "每辆车的最大载重量"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:40
msgid ":math:`d_i`"
msgstr ":math:`d_i`"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:41
msgid "Demand of customer :math:`i`"
msgstr "客户 :math:`i` 的需求量"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:42
msgid ":math:`d_i \\leq Q`; depot has :math:`d_0 = 0`"
msgstr ":math:`d_i \\leq Q`；仓库需求 :math:`d_0 = 0`"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:43
#, python-brace-format
msgid ":math:`c_{ij}`"
msgstr ":math:`c_{ij}`"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:44 ../../source/cvrp.rst:119
msgid "Distance"
msgstr "距离"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:45
msgid "Euclidean distance between nodes :math:`i` and :math:`j`"
msgstr "节点 :math:`i` 到节点 :math:`j` 的欧几里得距离"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:48
msgid "Constraints"
msgstr "约束条件"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:50
msgid "**Each route starts and ends at the depot**"
msgstr "**每条路线必须从仓库开始并结束**"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:52
msgid "Route form: depot → customer₁ → customer₂ → … → depot"
msgstr "路线形式：仓库 → 客户₁ → 客户₂ → … → 仓库"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:54
msgid "**Capacity constraint**"
msgstr "**容量约束**"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:56
msgid "Total demand on each route must not exceed vehicle capacity:"
msgstr "每条路线上所有客户的总需求不超过车辆容量："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:58
msgid "\\sum_{i \\in \\text{route}} d_i \\leq Q"
msgstr "\\sum_{i \\in \\text{route}} d_i \\leq Q"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:62
msgid "**Each customer is visited exactly once**"
msgstr "**每个客户被访问恰好一次**"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:64
msgid ""
"**Number of vehicles is unlimited** (but minimising vehicle count is "
"desirable)"
msgstr "**车辆数量不限** （但通常希望尽量少）"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:67
msgid "Objective"
msgstr "目标函数"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:69
msgid "Minimise total travel distance:"
msgstr "最小化总行驶距离："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:71
msgid "\\min \\sum_{k=1}^{K} \\sum_{(i,j) \\in \\text{route}_k} c_{ij}"
msgstr "\\min \\sum_{k=1}^{K} \\sum_{(i,j) \\in \\text{route}_k} c_{ij}"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:75
msgid "where :math:`K` is the number of vehicles used."
msgstr "其中 :math:`K` 是使用的车辆数。"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:78
msgid "Score Function"
msgstr "评分函数"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:80
msgid ""
"This project uses the following composite score to evaluate solver "
"performance:"
msgstr "本项目使用以下综合评分函数评估算法性能："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:82 ../../source/cvrp.rst:146
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\text{score} = \\text{avg\\_distance} + 20 \\times "
"\\text{avg\\_num\\_routes}"
msgstr ""
"\\text{score} = \\text{avg\\_distance} + 20 \\times "
"\\text{avg\\_num\\_routes}"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:86
msgid ""
"**Distance term**: average total route distance across instances — lower "
"is better"
msgstr "**距离项**：所有实例的平均总路径距离，越小越好"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:87
msgid "**Route count term**: average number of vehicles used — lower is better"
msgstr "**路线数项**：平均使用车辆数，越少越好"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:88
msgid "**Weight 20**: hyperparameter balancing the two objectives"
msgstr "**权重 20**：平衡两个目标的超参数"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:90
msgid "A lower score indicates better performance."
msgstr "评分越低表示算法性能越好。"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:93
msgid "Representation"
msgstr "表示方式"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:96
msgid "Route"
msgstr "路线"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:98
msgid ""
"A route is an ordered list of customer indices (integers), implicitly "
"starting and ending at the depot (node 0). The depot is **not** included "
"in the list."
msgstr "路线是客户索引（整数）的有序列表，隐式地从仓库（节点 0）出发并返回仓库。列表中 **不包含** 仓库节点。"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:105
msgid "A solution is a list of routes — one per vehicle used:"
msgstr "一个解由多条路线组成，每辆车对应一条路线："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:111
msgid "In code, these types are aliased as:"
msgstr "在代码中，这些类型定义为："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:121
msgid "All distances are **Euclidean** (straight-line) between 2-D coordinates:"
msgstr "所有距离均为二维坐标间的欧几里得距离（直线距离）："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:123
#, python-brace-format
msgid "c_{ij} = \\sqrt{(x_i - x_j)^2 + (y_i - y_j)^2}"
msgstr "c_{ij} = \\sqrt{(x_i - x_j)^2 + (y_i - y_j)^2}"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:127
msgid "The distance of a single route includes the return leg to the depot:"
msgstr "单条路线的距离包含返回仓库的行程："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:129
msgid ""
"\\text{dist}(\\text{route}) = c_{0,\\, r_1} + \\sum_{k=1}^{m-1} "
"c_{r_k,\\, r_{k+1}} + c_{r_m,\\, 0}"
msgstr ""
"\\text{dist}(\\text{route}) = c_{0,\\, r_1} + \\sum_{k=1}^{m-1} "
"c_{r_k,\\, r_{k+1}} + c_{r_m,\\, 0}"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:133
msgid "The total solution distance is the sum over all routes:"
msgstr "解的总距离为所有路线距离之和："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:135
#, python-brace-format
msgid "\\text{dist}(\\text{solution}) = \\sum_{k} \\text{dist}(\\text{route}_k)"
msgstr "\\text{dist}(\\text{solution}) = \\sum_{k} \\text{dist}(\\text{route}_k)"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:140
msgid "What makes a good solution?"
msgstr "什么是好的解？"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:142
msgid ""
"A solution is **feasible** if every customer is visited exactly once and "
"no route exceeds vehicle capacity. Among feasible solutions, a good one "
"minimises the composite score:"
msgstr "若每个客户恰好被访问一次且所有路线均不超过车辆容量，则该解是 **可行的**。在可行解中，好的解应使综合评分最小："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:150
msgid "Intuitively: short total travel distance with as few vehicles as possible."
msgstr "直观来说：在尽量少用车辆的前提下，使总行驶距离尽可能短。"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:153
msgid "What makes a good solver?"
msgstr "什么是好的求解器？"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:155
msgid ""
"A good solver produces low-score solutions consistently across instances "
"of varying size. Concretely, it should:"
msgstr "好的求解器能在不同规模的实例上稳定地产生低评分的解。具体而言，它应该："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:158
msgid "**Be fast** — practical solvers run in seconds, not hours"
msgstr "**速度快** — 实用求解器应在秒级内完成，而非数小时"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:159
msgid ""
"**Generalise** — perform well on both small and large instances without "
"tuning"
msgstr "**泛化性强** — 无需调参即可在小规模和大规模实例上均表现良好"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:160
msgid "**Be stable** — low variance across different random instances"
msgstr "**稳定性好** — 在不同随机实例上方差小"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:161
#, python-format
msgid ""
"**Approach optimality** — a Gap below ~10% is considered competitive for "
"heuristics"
msgstr "**接近最优** — Gap 低于约 10% 即被认为是有竞争力的启发式算法"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:164
msgid "Complexity"
msgstr "问题复杂度"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:166
msgid "CVRP is **NP-hard**:"
msgstr "CVRP 是 **NP-hard** 问题："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:168
msgid "The number of feasible solutions grows exponentially with :math:`n`"
msgstr "随着客户数 :math:`n` 增加，可行解数量呈指数增长"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:169
msgid "Exact solvers for :math:`n = 50` may take hours"
msgstr "对于 :math:`n = 50` 的问题，精确求解可能需要数小时"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:170
msgid "For large instances (:math:`n > 100`), heuristics are the practical choice"
msgstr "对于大规模问题（:math:`n > 100`），启发式算法是实用选择"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:173
msgid "Why is it hard?"
msgstr "为什么难？"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:175
msgid ""
"CVRP is a generalisation of the **Travelling Salesman Problem (TSP)**: if"
" you set vehicle capacity to infinity and use a single vehicle, CVRP "
"reduces exactly to TSP. Since TSP is already NP-hard, CVRP inherits that "
"hardness — and adds more on top."
msgstr ""
"CVRP 是 **旅行商问题（TSP）** 的推广：当车辆容量无限且只使用一辆车时，CVRP 退化为 TSP。由于 TSP 本身已是 NP-"
"hard，CVRP 继承了这一难度，并在此基础上更难。"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:179
msgid "The difficulty compounds from two sources:"
msgstr "难度来自两个相互叠加的因素："

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:181
msgid ""
"**Partitioning** — dividing :math:`n` customers into :math:`K` routes is "
"a set partition problem. The number of ways to do this grows as "
":math:`O(K^n)` (Stirling numbers of the second kind), which is super-"
"exponential in :math:`n`."
msgstr ""
"**划分** — 将 :math:`n` 个客户分配给 :math:`K` 条路线是一个集合划分问题。划分方案数以 "
":math:`O(K^n)`（第二类 Stirling 数）的速度增长，关于 :math:`n` 是超指数级的。"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:184
msgid ""
"**Routing** — once customers are assigned to a vehicle, finding the "
"optimal visit order within that route is itself a TSP. So you face an "
"exponential search inside each partition of an already exponential "
"partition space."
msgstr ""
"**路线排序** — 一旦客户被分配给某辆车，在该路线内寻找最优访问顺序本身就是一个 "
"TSP。因此，在已经是指数级的划分空间中，每个划分内部还需要进行指数级搜索。"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:187
msgid ""
"**Conflicting objectives** — minimising distance vs. minimising vehicle "
"count"
msgstr "**目标冲突** — 最短距离与最少车辆数相互制约"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:188
msgid "**Coupled constraints** — capacity limits and route planning interact"
msgstr "**约束耦合** — 容量约束与路径规划相互影响"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:191
msgid "References"
msgstr "参考文献"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:193
msgid ""
"**Dantzig & Ramser (1959)** — *\"The Truck Dispatching Problem\"* — "
"founding paper for CVRP"
msgstr ""
"**Dantzig & Ramser (1959)** — *\"The Truck Dispatching Problem\"* — CVRP "
"开创性论文"

#: ../../source/cvrp.rst:194
msgid ""
"**Clarke & Wright (1964)** — *\"Scheduling of Vehicles from a Central "
"Depot\"* — savings algorithm"
msgstr ""
"**Clarke & Wright (1964)** — *\"Scheduling of Vehicles from a Central "
"Depot\"* — 节约算法经典论文"

